as-de-la-india/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/visitar-el-taj-mahal/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/monumentos-de-la-india/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/visado-india-online-e-visa-para-india/", "#", "#Taj_Mahal_Negro_La_leyenda", "#El_Taj_Mahal", "#La_leyenda", "#El_Taj_Mahal_Negro_Indicios", "#Que_hay_de_verdad_en_la_leyenda", "#Mas_informacion_y_curiosidades_sobre_India", "https://laindiaincreible.com/visitar-agra-la-ciudad-del-taj-mahal/", "https://www.instagram.com/p/B9_2aLkldLH/?utm_source=ig_embed&utm_campaign=loading", "https://www.instagram.com/p/B9_2aLkldLH/?utm_source=ig_embed&utm_campaign=loading", "https://www.instagram.com/la_india_increible/?utm_source=ig_embed&utm_campaign=loading", "https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean-Baptiste_Tavernier", "https://viajairan.com/jardines-persas-en-iran/", "https://www.facebook.com/laindiaincreible/", "https://www.instagram.com/la_india_increible/", "https://bit.ly/Suscribiryoutube", "https://laindiaincreible.com/consejos-de-viaje-para-india/", "https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://laindiaincreible.com/taj-mahal-negro/", "https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://laindiaincreible.com/taj-mahal-negro/", "https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://laindiaincreible.com/taj-mahal-negro/&media=https://laindiaincreible.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Taj-Mahal-Negro-Agra.jpg&description=Taj%20Mahal%20Negro", "https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=*Taj%20Mahal%20Negro*nEn%20la%20India%20cuenta%20la%20leyenda%20que%20Sha%20Jahan%20I,%20el%20Emperador%20mogol%20que%20mand\u00f3%20construir%20el%20Taj%20Mahal%20para%20enterrar%20a%20su%20esposa,%20ten\u00eda%20planificado%20un%20hermano%20gemelo%20de%20esta%20maravilla%20del%20mundo%20al%20otro%20lado%20del%20r\u00edo%20Yamuna:%20El%20Taj%20Mahal%20Negro.%20Tenemos%20un%20post%20en%20el%20que%20te%20contamos%20toda%20la%20historia%20y%20como%20visitar%20el%20Taj%20Mahal%20original.%20Y%20tambi\u00e9n%20los%2015%20monumentos%20imprescindibles%20de%20la%20India.%20Si%20quieres%20visitar%20el%20pa\u00eds%20necesitar\u00e1s%20un%20Visado%20para%20la%20India.%20Contenido%20de%20este%20art\u00edculo%20ocultar%201%20Taj%20Mahal%20Negro:%20La%20leyenda%201.1%20El%20Taj%20Mahal%201.2%20La%20leyenda%202%20El%20Taj%20Mahal%20Negro:%20Indicios%202.1%20\u00bfQu\u00e9%20hay%20de%20verdad%20en%20la%20leyenda?%20Taj%20Mahal%20Negro:%20La%20leyenda%20Esta%20historia%20sostiene%20que%20el%20plan%20era%20construir%20un%20mausoleo%20id\u00e9ntico%20al%20Taj%20Mahal%20en%20la%20ribera%20opuesta%20del%20r\u00edo%20Yamuna.%20Pero%20en%20el%20hermano%20gemelo%20se%20cambiar\u00eda%20el%20m\u00e1rmol%20blanco%20del%20original%20por%20marmol%20negro.%20El%20Taj%20Mahal%20El%20Taj%20Mahal%20original%20es%20un%20conjunto%20de%20edificios%20construido%20entre%20los%20a\u00f1os%201631%20y%201648%20en%20Agra,%20en%20el%20actual%20Estado%20de%20Uttar%20Pradesh,%20en%20la%20India%20.%20Se%20encuentra,%20como%20comentamos%20a%20orillas%20del%20r\u00edo%20Yamuna,%20y%20fue%20encargado%20por%20orden%20del%20emperador%20musulm\u00e1n%20Shah%20Jahan%20de%20la%20dinast\u00eda%20mogola.%20El%20fascinante%20complejo%20se%20erigi\u00f3%20en%20honor%20de%20su%20esposa%20conocida%20como%20Mumtaz%20Mahal,%20fallecida%20en%20el%20parto%20al%20dar%20a%20luz%20a%20su%20decimocuarta%20hija.%20La%20leyenda%20En%201658%20el%20Emperador%20Sha%20Jahan%20fue%20destronado%20por%20su%20hijo\u00a0Aurangzeb%20y%20encerrado%20en%20el%20Fuerte%20de%20Agra.%20Esto%20impidi\u00f3%20que%20el%20Taj%20Mahal%20Negro%20se%20pudiese%20hacer%20realidad.%20Las%20grandes%20tumbas%20de%20los%20mogoles%20se%20situaban%20en%20jardines%20formando%20una%20cruz,%20con%20el%20mausoleo%20en%20el%20centro.%20Sin%20embargo,%20en%20el%20caso%20del%20Taj%20Mahal%20el%20mausoleo%20est\u00e1%20a%20un%20extremo%20de%20los%20jardines,%20formando%20una%20gran%20\u00abT\u00bb.%20Se%20puede%20observar%20incluso%20mirando%20Google%20Maps%20hoy%20en%20d\u00eda:%20Como%20se%20observa%20en%20la%20imagen%20a\u00e9rea%20otro%20edificio%20en%20la%20orilla%20de%20enfrente%20conseguir\u00eda%20una%20perfecta%20simetr\u00eda%20y%20un%20conjunto%20bell\u00edsimo.%20En%20este%20conjunto%20el%20propio%20r\u00edo%20formar\u00eda%20un%20canal%20central%20en%20un%20gigantesco%20jard\u00edn%20dividido%20en%20dos,%20con%20el%20Taj%20Mahal%20blanco%20al%20sur%20y%20el%20Taj%20Mahal%20negro%20al%20norte.%20El%20Taj%20Mahal%20Negro:%20Indicios%20El%20Taj%20Mahal%20que%20ha%20llegado%20a%20nuestros%20d\u00edas%20tiene%20la%20tumba%20de%20su%20esposa%20en%20el%20medio,%20por%20lo%20que%20era%20s\u00f3lo%20para%20ella.%20Cuando%20se%20visita%20el%20interior%20se%20observa%20que%20la%20tumba%20de%20Sha%20Jahan%20no%20\u00abencaja\u00bb.%20Esto%20fue%20porque%20fue%20a\u00f1adida%20posteriormente%20y%20no%20estaba%20en%20el%20plan.%20\u00bfQuiz\u00e1s%20su%20idea%20es%20ser%20enterrado%20en%20el%20Taj%20Mahal%20Negro?%20Otro%20indicio%20lo%20vemos%20en%20el%20mapa%20de%20arriba,%20donde%20claramente%20la%20planta%20de%20los%20jardines%20invita%20a%20pensar%20en%20otro%20edificio%20para%20hacerlo%20sim\u00e9trico.%20Adem\u00e1s%20al%20otro%20lado%20del%20r\u00edo%20se%20encontraron%20restos%20de%20m\u00e1rmol%20negro.%20\u00bfQu\u00e9%20hay%20de%20verdad%20en%20la%20leyenda?%20Pese%20a%20los%20indicios%20anteriores,%20la%20mayor%20parte%20de%20las%20pruebas%20actuales%20nos%20llevan%20a%20pensar%20que%20probablemente%20nunca%20existi\u00f3%20el%20plan%20para%20la%20construcci\u00f3n%20del%20Taj%20Mahal%20Negro.%20Para%20empezar,%20en%20la%20d\u00e9cada%20de%20los%2090%20se%20hicieron%20excavaciones%20que%20descubrieron%20que%20hab\u00eda%20algunas%20piezas%20de%20m\u00e1rmol%20negro,%20s\u00ed,%20pero%20que%20en%20realidad%20era%20m\u00e1rmol%20blanco%20que%20con%20el%20tiempo%20y%20las%20condiciones%20clim\u00e1ticas%20se%20hab\u00eda%20vuelto%20negro.%20Pero%20la%20realidad%20es%20que%20los%20arque\u00f3logos%20nunca%20encontraron%20m\u00e1rmol%20negro.%20Parece%20ser%20que%20el%20origen%20de%20la%20leyenda%20son%20unos%20relatos%20de%20un%20viajero%20franc\u00e9s%20que%20viaj\u00f3%20a%20Persia%20e%20India,%20y%20visit\u00f3%20Agra%20en%201665,\u00a0Jean-Baptiste%20Tavernier.%20Pero%20se%20cree%20que%20muchos%20de%20sus%20relatos%20eran%20fant\u00e1sticos.%20La%20opini\u00f3n%20m\u00e1s%20generalizada%20es%20que%20la%20idea%20era%20la%20creaci\u00f3n%20de%20un%20jard\u00edn%20en%20la%20otra%20orilla%20del%20r\u00edo%20Yamuna%20para%20mantener%20la%20apreciada%20simetr\u00eda%20de%20los%20jardines%20persas.%20Los%20arque\u00f3logos%20han%20llamado%20a%20este%20segundo%20y%20nunca%20construido%20Taj,%20como%20el\u00a0Mahtab%20Bagh.%20La%20idea%20es%20que%20tuviese%20una%20gran%20piscina%20donde%20se%20reflejar\u00eda%20la%20imagen%20del%20Taj%20Mahal,%20que%20parecer\u00eda%20de%20color%20negro.%20Quiz\u00e1s%20de%20ah\u00ed%20la%20confusi\u00f3n%20y%20el%20nacimiento%20de%20la%20historia.%20La%20verdad%20es%20que%20nunca%20sabremos%20a%20ciencia%20cierta%20si%20por%20la%20cabeza%20del%20Emperador%20pas\u00f3%20la%20idea%20de%20construir%20el%20Taj%20Negro.%20\u200bnhttps://laindiaincreible.com/taj-mahal-negro/", "http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https://laindiaincreible.com/taj-mahal-negro/&title=Taj%20Mahal%20Negro", "https://laindiaincreible.com/templo-de-akshardham/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/visitar-nueva-delhi/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/visitar-jaisalmer-la-ciudad-dorada/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/visitar-jaisalmer-la-ciudad-dorada/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/playas-de-goa-india/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/playas-de-goa-india/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/tumba-de-safdarjung/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/tumba-de-safdarjung/", "http://Colinaangel557@gmail.com", " https://laindiaincreible.com/taj-mahal-negro/#comment-7013 ", "#comment-7013", "/taj-mahal-negro/#respond", "https://akismet.com/privacy/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/tours-india/", "https://laindiaincreible.com/tours-india/norte-de-india